The Calvin Bryce Hoover papers span the years
		  1922-1970, with the bulk falling between 1929 and 1968. The
		  collection is arranged into nine series:
		  Correspondence;
		  Writings;
		  Academic Materials;
		  Professional Associations;
		  Government Service;
		  Subject Files;
		  Audio-Visual Material;
		  Personal; and
		  Printed Material. The
		  collection includes correspondence, departmental files,
		  reports, photographs, sound recordings, books, articles,
		  clippings, scrapbooks, date books, and other printed
		  materials.
